{
  "name": "Pyromania: Trial By Fire",
  "shortName": "pyromania-trial-by-fire",
  "description": "In this retro cross between <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Q%2abert\">Q*Bert</a>, <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Crush+Roller\">Make Trax</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Pac-Man\">Pac-Man</a>, a single player controls a pyromaniac in a little van trying to destroy all those pesky creatures. But, every time you complete one of the eight levels, a different challenge awaits you. On odd-numbered levels (except level seven), the player must create fire to kill all the enemies, and on even-numbered levels (and level seven), the player must find the exit. But the obstacles in the player's way change every time - for example, in one level, he/she must find all the gas canisters, and in another, he/she must find fire tiles to roast enemies. Also, in another retro touch, each of the stages is patterned after a retro game of the 1980's era.",
